The '''Listian Hills''' were a range of low mountains located on the dark, murky [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Barab I/Legends|Barab I]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]]. [[Barabel/Legends|Barabel]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Saba Sebatyne]] and a native of Barab I often traveled to the hills in her youth.

